source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 2003 through September 30, 2004
source.description: This file contains the National Science Foundation (NSF)'s 2004 Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2004. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
